== 制作 ==
2014年5月2日，据宣布[[伍迪·艾伦|伍迪·艾伦]]将为[[杰昆·菲尼克斯|杰昆·菲尼克斯]]出演的电影编剧、导演<ref name=Phoenix>{{cite news |last1=Fleming Jr |first1=Mike |title=Joaquin Phoenix Set For Starring Role In Next Woody Allen Movie |url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/05/joaquin-phoenix-in-next-woody-allen-movie |accessdate=2014-07-08 |publisher=Deadline.com |date=2014-05-02 |archive-date=2014-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140708235005/http://www.deadline.com/2014/05/joaquin-phoenix-in-next-woody-allen-movie/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。5月6日，[[艾玛·斯通|艾玛·斯通]]加盟剧组，该片自此成为她继2014年的《[[魔力月光|魔力月光]]》后，第二部艾伦电影<ref name=Stone>{{cite news |last1=Kroll |first1=Justin |title=Emma Stone Joins Joaquin Phoenix in Woody Allen's Next Film |url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/emma-stone-joaquin-phoenix-woody-allen-1201172304 |accessdate=2014-07-08 |work=Variety |date=2014-05-06 |archive-date=2021-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324134722/https://variety.com/2014/film/news/emma-stone-joaquin-phoenix-woody-allen-1201172304/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。7月24日，[[帕克·波西|帕克·波西]]和{{le|杰米·布莱克利|Jamie Blackley}}加盟剧组，艾伦也与姐妹{{le|蕾蒂·阿隆森|Letty Aronson}}和{{le|斯蒂芬·特南鲍姆|Stephen Tenenbaum}}共同出任制作人<ref name="Posey-Blackley">{{cite news|last1=Kroll|first1=Justin|title=Parker Posey and Jamie Blackley Join Woody Allen’s Next Film|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/parker-posey-jamie-blackley-woody-allen-1201268380|accessdate=2014-07-28|work=Variety|date=2014-07-24|archive-date=2019-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191229235122/https://variety.com/2014/film/news/parker-posey-jamie-blackley-woody-allen-1201268380/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年1月29日，[[索尼经典电影|索尼经典电影]]收购电影发行权，并透露片名为《无理之人》<ref>{{cite news|last1=McNary|first1=Dave|title=Sony Classics Buys Woody Allen's ''Irrational Man'' for North America|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/sony-classics-buys-woody-allens-irrational-man-for-north-america-1201418954|accessdate=2015-01-30|work=Variety|date=2015-01-29|archive-date=2020-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926215205/https://variety.com/2015/film/news/sony-classics-buys-woody-allens-irrational-man-for-north-america-1201418954/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年7月7日，影片于[[罗德岛州|罗德岛州]][[纽波特_(罗德岛州)|纽波特]]开拍，8月底杀青<ref>{{cite news |title=Woody Allen Film in RI Begins Production |url=http://www.golocalprov.com/lifestyle/wody-allen-film-in-ri-begins-production |accessdate=2014-07-08 |publisher=GoLocalProv.com |date=2014-07-07 |archive-date=2020-02-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200229131756/https://www.golocalprov.com/lifestyle/wody-allen-film-in-ri-begins-production |dead-url=no }}</ref>。剧组曾现身纽波特法斯特耐特酒吧（{{lang|en|The Fastnet Pub}}）外拍戏<ref>{{cite news |last1=Squires |first1=Frieda |title=Woody Allen project filming in Newport |url=http://www.providencejournal.com/breaking-news/content/20140707-photo-woody-allen-project-filming-in-newport.ece |accessdate=2014-07-08 |work=The Providence Journal |date=2014-07-07 |archive-date=2019-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191208004117/https://www.providencejournal.com/breaking-news/content/20140707-photo-woody-allen-project-filming-in-newport.ece |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Goldstein |first1=Meredith |last2=Shanahan |first2=Mark |title=Emma Stone stays in Rhode Island for Woody Allen film |url=http://www.bostonglobe.com/lifestyle/names/2014/07/07/emma-stone-stays-rhode-island-for-woody-allen-film/kSc6tJuk7vMXG6UhGhMQaI/story.html |accessdate=2014-07-08 |work=The Boston Globe |date=2014-07-08 |archive-date=2021-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119172518/https://www.bostonglobe.com/lifestyle/names/2014/07/07/emma-stone-stays-rhode-island-for-woody-allen-film/kSc6tJuk7vMXG6UhGhMQaI/story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 发行 ==
[[File:Cannes_2015_4.jpg|thumb]]、[[伍迪·艾伦|伍迪·艾伦]]和[[帕克·波西|帕克·波西]]于[[2015年戛纳电影节|2015年戛纳电影节]]上宣传影片。]]

影片是[[索尼经典电影|索尼经典电影]]发行的第八部伍迪·艾伦电影<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/sony-classics-buys-woody-allens-irrational-man-for-north-america-1201418954/|title=Sony Classics Buys Woody Allen’s ‘Irrational Man’ for North America|author=Dave McNary|work=Variety|access-date=2016-07-30|archive-date=2020-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926215205/https://variety.com/2015/film/news/sony-classics-buys-woody-allens-irrational-man-for-north-america-1201418954/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。影片首支[[预告片|预告片]]于2015年4月29日发行<ref>{{cite web |author=Alexandra Sifferlin |url=http://time.com/3840747/woody-allen-irrational-man-trailer |title=Watch the Trailer for Woody Allen Film, Emma Stone and Joaquin Phoenix |work=Time |date=2015-04-29 |accessdate=2015-05-18 |archive-date=2020-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919090234/https://time.com/3840747/woody-allen-irrational-man-trailer/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，2015年5月16日在[[戛纳电影节|戛纳电影节]]全球首映<ref name="variety1">{{cite web |author=Scott Foundas |url=http://variety.com/2015/film/reviews/irrational-man-cannes-review-1201496955 |title=''Irrational Man'' Review: Woody And Joaquin Plot The Perfect Murder |work=Variety |date=2015-05-06 |accessdate=2015-05-18 |archive-date=2020-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210050002/https://variety.com/2015/film/reviews/irrational-man-cannes-review-1201496955/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，2015年7月17日[[有限上映|有限上映]]<ref>{{cite web |author=Maane Khatchatourian |url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/first-look-emma-stone-joaquin-phoenix-in-woody-allens-irrational-man-1201470803 |title=Emma Stone in Woody Allen's ''Irrational Man'' |work=Variety |date=2015-04-11 |accessdate=2015-05-18 |archive-date=2020-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200114094714/https://variety.com/2015/film/news/first-look-emma-stone-joaquin-phoenix-in-woody-allens-irrational-man-1201470803/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，后来于2015年8月7日{{le|大规模上映|Wide release}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2015/07/mr-holmes-ian-mckellen-irrational-man-woody-allen-specialty-box-office-1201482032/ |title='Mr. Holmes' Dominates, 'Irrational Man' Debut Solid: Specialty B.O. |author=Brian Brooks |publisher=Deadline.com |date=2015-07-19 |accessdate=2016-07-29 |archive-date=2021-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211204722/https://deadline.com/2015/07/mr-holmes-ian-mckellen-irrational-man-woody-allen-specialty-box-office-1201482032/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，并于9月24日和11月20日登陆香港和台湾<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lGa5Cl3M9Kw |title=《情迷失控點》(Irrational Man) 正式預告片9月24日上映 |website=Youtube |date=2015-08-17 |accessdate=2016-07-29}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hLVRKMQq_Cs |title=《愛情失控點》 電影預告11.20上映 |work=YouTube |date=2015-10-15 |accessdate=2016-07-29 |archive-date=2020-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027101548/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hLVRKMQq_Cs |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 评价 ==
影片获得影评人褒贬不一的评价。在{{le|评论聚合|Review aggregator}}网站[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]上，根据176条评论，影片获得44%的新鲜度，平均得分5.4（满分10）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/irrational_man/ |title=Irrational Man |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2015-09-14 |archive-date=2016-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160510220256/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/irrational_man |dead-url=no }}</ref>。网站公示指出：“《无理之人》对于杰昆·菲尼克斯的最热心影迷或为伍迪·艾伦辩解的人来说是回报，但对大多数人来说可能没有什么感受。”[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]则根据53条评论打出53分，表示“好坏参半”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/irrational-man|title=Irrational Man reviews|publisher=Metacritic|accessdate=2015-09-10|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112015312/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/irrational-man|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《[[好莱坞报道者|好莱坞报道者]]》的大卫·鲁尼（{{lang|en|David Ronney}}）打出90分，他指出：“艾伦的对白很机智，他在所有恰当的地方布下兴奋点，推动剧情前进，他对弹性道德原则的观察不断变化，是既调皮又让人不安，产生出结局处希区柯克式的美味扭曲<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movie/irrational-man/review/795347 |title='Irrational Man': Cannes Review |publisher=The Hollywood Report |date=2015-05-15 |accessdate=2016-07-30 |archive-date=2015-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151017012507/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movie/irrational-man/review/795347 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”而《The Playlist》的杰西卡·江（{{lang|en|Jessica Kiang}}）则打出33分，他认为：“搞笑程度不足以成为喜剧，剧情不足以成为一部惊悚片，智慧得不孚众望，只有艾比·卢卡斯支持<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.indiewire.com/2015/05/cannes-review-woody-allens-irrational-man-starring-joaquin-phoenix-emma-stone-and-parker-posey-263995/|title=Cannes Review: Woody Allen’s ‘Irrational Man’ Starring Joaquin Phoenix, Emma Stone And Parker Posey|publisher=Indie Wire|date=2015-05-15|accessdate=2016-07-30|archive-date=2020-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130060440/https://www.indiewire.com/2015/05/cannes-review-woody-allens-irrational-man-starring-joaquin-phoenix-emma-stone-and-parker-posey-263995/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

